00:24:04,333 --> 00:24:05,366
Average.

451
00:24:05,433 --> 00:24:06,033
D.

452
00:24:06,100 --> 00:24:06,800
You're in trouble.

453
00:24:06,866 --> 00:24:07,433
E.

